text:
Ah! That's the issue! The API key is for **international** region but I'm using the **China mainland endpoint**. For international DashScope API keys, I need to use the **Singapore endpoint**.

Let me fix this by updating the API endpoint from:
- ❌ `https://dashscope.aliyuncs.com/compatible-mode/v1` (China mainland)
- ✅ `https://dashscope-intl.aliyuncs.com/compatible-mode/v1` (International/Singapore)
